column5: going to sioux lookout for the walleye tournament never fished there in my life and info on the lake is greatly appreciated
Be carefull its worse than the west end of lac seul.when going from abram to minnitaki through the shuts stay tight to the rock wall.its spooky the first time.abeam has good fish to.
